into halves","4 garlic cloves","4 - 6 long red chillies, deseeded if preferred, adjust to taste","½ - 1 tsp chilli powder","2 tbsp extra virgin olive oil","400 g canned kidney beans, drained and rinsed","400 g canned chopped tomatoes","4 tbsp tomato paste","2 tbsp vegetable stock paste"]}],"id":"r68546","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-f1VSv3FTyzM\/XZQvP_pr4nI\/AAAAAAAAcbg\/zNNXJ1pLgdsQh5mW7Bee3U6XuQhYe4enwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Djb1IEZ9EzCxujw9.png","title":"Chilli con carne","publishedAt":"2014-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"28 g","fat":"13 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"20 g","calories":"1397 kJ \/ 332 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","6 portions"]}